a15 Directory Reference

Directories

directory  V0
 

Files

file  cache_a15.h
 This file contains the interfaces present in the A15 Cache HAL. This also contains some related macros, structures and enums.
 
file  cache_a15_gcc_asm.h
 This file contains the function declarations for ASM APIs needed by the A15 Cache HAL.
 
file  cache_a15_rom_api_calls_asm.h
 This file contains the function declarations for ASM APIs needed by the A15 ROM API calls.
 
file  cp15.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring CP15.
 
file  cpu.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring CPU.
 
file  arch/a15/csl_a15_startup.h
 
file  ecc_a15.h
 This file contains the interfaces present in the A15 ECC HAL. This also contains some related macros, structures and enums.
 
file  ecc_a15_gcc_asm.h
 This file contains the function declarations for ASM APIs needed by the A15 ECC HAL.
 
file  hw_intc.h
 This file contains the MACROS definitions used by interrupt controller module.
 
file  hw_mpu_intc_dist.h
 register-level header file for MPU
 
file  hw_mpu_intc_phys.h
 register-level header file for MPU
 
file  hw_mpu_wugen.h
 register-level header file for MPU
 
file  a15/interrupt.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring INTC for ARM Cortex-A15.
 
file  mmu_a15.h
 This file contains the interfaces present in the A15 MMU HAL. This also contains some related macros, structures and enums. This implementation supports only two levels of translation tables. Physical address is 40 bits long instead of 32 bits.
 
file  mmu_a15_gcc_asm.h
 This file contains the function declarations for ASM APIs needed by the A15 MMU HAL.
 
file  mpu_wugen.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring MPU_WUGEN for ARM Cortex-A15 on AM57x and TDA2xx SOC's.
